---
title: Teriyaki & Ginger Beef Stir-Fry with Sesame Dressing & Crispy Shallots
description: A beef stir-fry isn’t complete without veggies and a sticky dark sauce. Make sure it coats everything, and use that rice to soak it up - you don’t want to leave a drop of this punchy flavour combo in the bowl!
